fablab school transformative learning technologies laboratory home about publications projects people teaching media fablearn 2011 home tltl in the news fablab school fablab school image the first fablab school was inaugurated in june 2011 at the 1502 imei high school in moscow russia following up on the pilot version built at stanford at the beginning of 2009 the first fablab school has opened in june 2011 at the 1502 imei high school in moscow russia the lab is equipped with computer controlled tools such as laser cutters routing machines 3d scanners 3d milling machines and programming tools and aims to stimulate interest in steam sciences technology engineering art and math subjects among students who previously lacked access to facilities or did not believe they had talent in these fields the ability to make almost anything in a hands on learning environment will provide an opportunity for students to engage in cutting edge scientific investigation this is a tv report about the inauguration remember to turn on captions on youtube transformative learning technologies lab school of education stanford university 520 galvez mall room 102 ceras building stanford california 94305 usa connect with us connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr copyright 2011 all rights reserved top
